  <brief_title>Hybrid PET/CT in Cancer Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Value of Novel Imaging Modality, Hybrid PET/CT, Using F18-Flurodeoxyglucose(FDG) in the Assessment of Cancer Patients. Impact of PET/CT on Clinical Management of Patients With Rising Tumor Markers and no Other Evidence of Disease and in Patients With Metastatic Cancer of Unknown Origin</official_title>
  <sponsors>
